"[collections](../module-reference/utility-modules/shared/collections.md)\n"
": Filtrer la liste des images affichées dans la vue carte.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/map/map-view-layout.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Here you can find the modules specific to the map view. From top to bottom:\n"
msgstr "Ici vous trouvez les modules spécifiques à la vue carte. De haut en bas :\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/map/map-view-layout.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[find location](../module-reference/utility-modules/map/find-location.md)\n"
": Search for a place on map.\n"
msgstr ""
"[trouver un lieu](../module-reference/utility-modules/map/find-location.md)\n"
": Rechercher un lieu sur la carte\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/map/map-view-layout.md
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"[locations](../module-reference/utility-modules/map/locations.md)\n"
": Manage a hierarchical list of location tags and their corresponding regions on the map.\n"
msgstr ""
"[emplacements](../module-reference/utility-modules/map/locations.md)\n"
