#: content/module-reference/processing-modules/tone-curve.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "tone curve"
msgstr "courbe des tonalités"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/processing-modules/tone-curve.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "A classic digital photography tool to alter the tones of an image's using curves.\n"
