#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/shared/focus-peaking.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "focus peaking"
msgstr "détection de focus"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/shared/focus-peaking.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Identify which parts of the image contain sharp edges, which usually indicates that those areas are in focus.\n"
msgstr "Identifie quelles parties de l'image contiennent des bords nets, ce qui indique généralement que ces zones sont au point.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/shared/focus-peaking.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Activate the module by clicking on the ![focus-peaking-icon](./focus-peaking/focus-peaking-icon.png#icon) icon. The sharp parts of the image will be highlighted with a yellow, green and blue overlay:\n"
msgstr "Le module s'active en cliquant sur l'icône (![focus-peaking-icon](./focus-peaking/focus-peaking-icon.png#icon)). Il met en évidence les parties nettes de l'image avec un affichage en surbrillance jaune, vert et bleu :\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/shared/focus-peaking.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "Focus peaking works by filtering out image noise, measuring the intensity gradients in the image and calculating average and standard deviation statistics. When the gradient of an edge differs significantly from the mean, the associated pixels are marked with a \"heat map\" indicating how sharp the edge is.\n"
msgstr "Le module fonctionne en filtrant le bruit de l'image, en mesurant les gradients d'intensité dans l'image et en calculant des statistiques de moyenne et d'écart type. Lorsque le gradient d'un bord diffère significativement de la moyenne, les pixels associés sont marqués d'une \"carte thermique\" indiquant la netteté du bord.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/shared/focus-peaking.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "_yellow_ represents a large (6σ) jump in gradient, indicating a very sharp edge.\n"
msgstr "Le _jaune_ représente un fort gradient (6σ), indiquant un bord très net.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/shared/focus-peaking.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "_green_ represents a medium (4σ) jump in gradient, indicating a reasonably sharp edge.\n"
msgstr "Le _vert_ représente un gradient moyen (4σ), indiquant un bord assez net.\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/shared/focus-peaking.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "_blue_ represents a small (2σ) jump in gradient, indicating a slightly sharp edge.\n"
msgstr "Le _bleu_ représente un gradient faible, indiquant un bord légèrement net.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/shared/focus-peaking.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "![focus-peaking-overview](./focus-peaking/focus-peaking-overview.png#w75)\n"
msgstr "![focus-peaking-overview](./focus-peaking/focus-peaking-overview.png#w75)\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/shared/focus-peaking.md
#, no-wrap
msgid "The image above was taken with a wide aperture to give a shallow depth of field, and you can see how the camera has focused on the chinese character written on the second red lantern along from the front. There are also stems of the pink flowers that fall within the area of acceptable sharpness around the focal plane, and these have also been marked up with yellow and green.\n"
msgstr "L'image ci-dessus a été prise avec une grande ouverture pour obtenir une faible profondeur de champ, et vous pouvez voir comment l'appareil photo a fait la mise au point sur le caractère chinois écrit sur la deuxième lanterne rouge en partant de l'avant. Il y a également des tiges de fleurs roses qui se trouvent dans la zone de netteté acceptable autour du plan focal, et celles-ci sont également marquées de jaune et de vert.\n"

#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: content/module-reference/utility-modules/shared/metadata-editor.md
